# Project Context

## What This Is

Loomernescent v2 — a NestJS v11 rebuild of a legacy Express 4 / Mongoose / MongoDB SSR shoegaze music site. SSR with Pug (not a REST API). TypeORM + PostgreSQL (Neon) replacing Mongoose/MongoDB.

## Legacy Reference Codebase

The original app lives at `/Users/thomasbullock/Sites/Loomer-Redux/loomernescent/` (adjacent to this project). Use it as reference for:

- Original Pug templates (`loomernescent/views/`)
- Original SCSS (`loomernescent/public/sass/`)
- Mongoose schemas → map to TypeORM entities (`loomernescent/models/`)
- Express controllers/routes → map to Nest controllers/services (`loomernescent/controllers/`, `loomernescent/routes/`)
- Handler logic (upload, Spotify, etc.) (`loomernescent/handlers/`)
- JSON data fixtures used by the seed script (`loomernescent/data/`)

**Do not copy legacy patterns verbatim** — port to NestJS/TypeORM idioms. The legacy stack (Webpack 2, Babel 6, Passport 0.3, express-validator 3, Mongoose) is outdated and will NOT be replicated.

## Stack Decisions (fixed)

- **Framework:** NestJS v11 on Express adapter (`NestExpressApplication`)
- **Templates:** Pug (SSR via `@Render()` decorator, not REST API)
- **ORM:** TypeORM (no Mongoose)
- **DB:** PostgreSQL on Neon (SSL required, branches for dev/prod)
- **Styles:** SCSS via Dart `sass` CLI (no Webpack); Tailwind migration is a later phase
- **Slug generation:** `slugify` package (not legacy `slugs`)
- **Config:** `@nestjs/config` with `.env`

## Phase 1 — Complete

Foundation for rendering styled pages backed by a real DB. Delivered:

- `src/main.ts` — Pug engine, views dir, static assets mount (`public/`)
- `src/app.module.ts` — `ConfigModule`, `TypeOrmModule.forRootAsync`, domain modules, `TemplateLocalsMiddleware` on all routes
- `src/entities/` — `User`, `Band`, `Album`, `Pedal`, `Favourite` (UUID PKs, snake_case DB columns, typed relations)
- `src/bands/`, `src/albums/`, `src/pedals/` — module + controller + service per domain
- `src/common/helpers/template-helpers.ts` — `siteName`, `menu`, `icon()` (cached SVG read), `buildDatesString()`, `dump()`, `staticMap()`
- `src/common/middleware/template-locals.middleware.ts` — injects `h`, `currentPath`, `path`, `user`, `flashes` into `res.locals`
- `src/styles/` — all legacy SCSS partials + vendored Bourbon; compiles to `public/dist/style.css`
- `views/` — all legacy Pug templates (some for future phases not yet wired to routes)
- `src/data-source.ts` + `src/migrations/` — TypeORM CLI wiring
- `src/seeds/seed.ts` — reads `/loomernescent/data/` JSON fixtures, maps ObjectIds→UUIDs, resolves image filenames

**Phase 1 routes (read-only):** `/`, `/bands`, `/bands/page/:page`, `/band/:slug`, `/albums`, `/album/:slug`, `/pedals`, `/pedal/:slug`.

Phase 1 plan (full detail): `/Users/thomasbullock/.claude/plans/unified-doodling-origami.md`

## Not Yet Built (future phases)

Templates for these exist in `views/` but have no routes or services yet:

- **Auth** — login, register, password reset with token flow, guards (legacy uses Passport — port to Nest-native or `@nestjs/passport`)
- **File upload + image resizing** — band/album/pedal photos (legacy uses `multer` + `jimp`)
- **Spotify integration** — fetch album/artist data
- **Favourites (loves)** — toggle, favourites page
- **Geospatial / map** — band locations; deferred PostGIS + map page
- **Full-text search** — tsvector/GIN; typeahead
- **Admin forms** — add/edit band, album, pedal
- **Client-side JS** — typeahead, modals, lazy loading, map interactions (Vite may be introduced when needed)
- **Tailwind migration** — after feature parity is reached

When building these, check the legacy codebase for the intended behaviour first, then design the Nest/TypeORM equivalent.
